*libesmtp-1.0.3 (03 Sep 2004)

  03 Sep 2004; Andrej Kacian <ticho@gentoo.org> metadata.xml,
  +libesmtp-1.0.3.ebuild:
  Version bump. Reported by Torsten Stets <mai98bmg@studserv.uni-leipzig.de>,
  closing #57194. Use ${PN} in SRC_URI and HOMEPAGE for all libesmtp ebuilds.

  13 Apr 2004; Danny van Dyk <kugelfang@gentoo.org> libesmtp-1.0.1.ebuild:
  marked ~amd64

